Give it here.

196
00:12:07,159 --> 00:12:08,120
Give it back.

197
00:12:13,039 --> 00:12:14,159
Return her hair clip.

198
00:12:14,559 --> 00:12:15,840
Mind your own business.

199
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:17,080
Get out of our way.

200
00:12:18,519 --> 00:12:19,879
(I got into a fight today)

201
00:12:20,879 --> 00:12:22,039
(because of you.)

202
00:12:22,799 --> 00:12:24,799
(I won't let anyone bully you.)

203
00:12:26,399 --> 00:12:28,919
(But I couldn't win.)

204
00:12:28,919 --> 00:12:31,600
(Even the hair clip I finally got back)

205
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:32,600
(is broken.)

206
00:12:33,740 --> 00:12:38,980
♪Can contain you♪

207
00:12:43,039 --> 00:12:44,559
(We grew up.)

208
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:47,679
(Still, I couldn't save enough money)

209
00:12:48,679 --> 00:12:50,279
(to buy her one just like it.)

210
00:12:53,460 --> 00:12:58,980
♪But that abyss is our reunion♪

211
00:12:59,399 --> 00:13:01,000
If you're here to avenge
your father's death,

212
00:13:01,559 --> 00:13:02,679
you'd better stop.

213
00:13:10,240 --> 00:13:11,399
(So in the previous life,)

214
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:14,000
(he really did want to save me.)

215
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:17,000
(April 30, stormy rain)

216
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:18,440
(I never thought you'd follow me here.)

217
00:13:19,159 --> 00:13:20,320
I promised to bring you here,

218
00:13:21,399 --> 00:13:22,759
not take you inside.

219
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:24,799
(It's too dangerous upstairs.)

220
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:26,679
(I can't let you go.)

221
00:13:30,159 --> 00:13:31,919
(Even in this life,)

222
00:13:31,919 --> 00:13:33,799
(he's been protecting me.)

223
00:13:40,039 --> 00:13:42,000
(This shot won't kill you.)

224
00:13:42,720 --> 00:13:44,240
(I hope you survive this.)

225
00:13:47,879 --> 00:13:49,279
(I wanted to save Mr. Zhao,)

226
00:13:51,039 --> 00:13:52,519
(but I couldn't stop Zhen.)

227
00:13:54,679 --> 00:13:55,480
(I'm sorry.)

228
00:13:56,679 --> 00:13:57,799
(I'm useless.)

229
