Whose clothes are these?

230
00:14:09,159 --> 00:14:10,399
My brother's.

231
00:14:13,559 --> 00:14:14,360
What's wrong?

232
00:14:17,039 --> 00:14:17,840
Silly.

233
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:21,559
What are you talking about?

234
00:14:22,799 --> 00:14:23,759
