235
00:14:35,039 --> 00:14:36,200
You're silly.

236
00:14:44,799 --> 00:14:46,240
I didn't expect you

237
00:14:46,240 --> 00:14:47,799
to be reading my diary.

238
00:14:48,220 --> 00:14:53,180
♪You left me a piece
to teach me to savor repeatedly♪

239
